I know this mix is called Sunday Morning and that i'm currently posting this Monday morning ....but regardless i really hope you guys enjoy this chill/feels mix <3   I started this back in July but was really busy with work / other show / vacation, so I'm uploading this right before i head back to school!  The vibe this mix gives me is the feeling of sleeping in and chilling in bed for a solid hour after waking up on Sunday, right before u gotta start all ur work/errands LOL.  Anyways, school's starting so ima get busy again but thanks for sticking with me even through my less active phases everyone <3 <3 it really means alot and ily all hehe

Tracklist: https://twitter.com/ayykeri/status/1055627003091595264
Hey guys :) I know it's been a loooong ass time and I'm sorry I didn't get to release a september mix :(  Life and school have been pretty busy/stressful and I struggled with finding motivation for a really long time but I'm really happy with how this mix turned out!  
This mix is special to me since it has a pretty different vibe from the other mixes I've made, and it's my first time putting in some r&b in a mix too.  I'm trying to branch out of my comfort zone and experiment by making mixes of other genres, so I really hope you guys like this and if you have any other genres you think I should try lemme know!  I also might slow down making mixes to focus on producing/school , so I'm sorry if I'm not as active as I used to be - I still really enjoy showing you guys my music and I'm really thankful for your guys' kind messages and reminders to get my ass on making my next mix LOL.  

SPECIAL SHOUTOUT TO MAH HOUSEMATE @cayleyhohoho for making dis pic for me hehe <3 
Anyways, love u guys and thanks for listening! - Kelly

description:
Porter and Illenium are the artists that really got me into EDM 3 years ago, and I don't even know how many times I've listened to their albums and simped like crazy.  I was a bit hesitant making this mix since nowadays so many of their fans are pegged as "basic," but honestly their music is freaking amazing, which is why they're so beloved.  I made this mix as a tribute to the 2 artists I look up to the most, and I know you guys have heard these songs a thousand times by now so I hope you guys enjoy all the edits I made in order to give this mix a bit of my own personality :).  Hope you guys enjoy, and I hope this helps with that audio comedown cuz man i feel that LOL
I make mixes monthly! Check them out: https://soundcloud.com/heykeri/sets/heykeri-monthly-mixes
